elements.2211.03040_62fcdb090b826c3e989d4528fad52: Long-Short-Term-Memory Nonlinear Autoregressive Exogenous Neural Network Overview
elements.2211.03040_e47bf1bb577151780e368026766bf: A black-box system is a structure with unknown topology and/or characteristics, whose input and output signals are often interpreted
elements.2211.03040_600909b86302881efe78fc3af4ed7: In general, the outputs are the consequence of an excitation or stimulation applied in the form of input values or vectors to the black box
elements.2211.03040_e02a000d7dfdb2ec9a7d715218900: Estimating the topology and parameters of a system when just its input and output values are known is not a simple issue
elements.2211.03040_758931abe12179466c5b4c6b1d1d4: Long-Short-Term-Memory (LSTM) functions as a model for the dynamics of a system
elements.2211.03040_420fc52caa540678a2ea5a0ad0373: LSTM's are distinguished by the fact that their output variables are sent back to the system's input
elements.2211.03040_a6333385afe0d4e0631850971a3af: A LSTM NARX NN (or NARX-LSTM) is a solution for identifying the performance of a black-box system
elements.2211.03040_5536a077cabf1b37ab4dccf5bcec6: Based on the expansion of historical inputs and outputs, it can anticipate the outcome of a nonlinear system
elements.2211.03040_c9097d94cfe8e9521f97ce1697756: The model is specified by either of the two following equations, which depend on the system's configuration:

elements.2211.03040_0ef358b7b069b1a7dec92711bfc0b: The two designs of the NARX-LSTM system, given by equations (1) and (2), rely on whether or not the output information is sent back
elements.2211.03040_3482f29c0d665569da203edf8f255: The open loop (or series) architecture is commonly used for designing and training neural networks since it estimates the output of the system based on a priori (known) target information (predicted)
elements.2211.03040_1ae61cdc53955afb5c2d5ca5287b4: The closed loop design, on the other hand, uses the actual estimated output as an input to the black box, therefore it is not necessary to obtain the desired data beforehand, which is advantageous for predictions

elements.2211.03040_1025d503c00397df9dd37e39feefb: The input and output variables of the black-box system were selected with the knowledge that the trained NARX-LSTM mimics the behavior of a DC-DC power converter
elements.2211.03040_c53a2de38478f89befc7cecb58126: The only accessible data then, assuming the topology of the converter is unknown, are the current and voltage measurements at the input and output terminals of the circuit
elements.2211.03040_a85579158478c7565c33ba19306b3: However, the input and output variable values of the converter do not always correspond to those of the NARX neural network
elements.2211.03040_a38719d163b06fb0f9c173f459a6b: In light of the fact that the variables may be altered externally, the black-box signals for this particular situation are categorized as follows:
elements.2211.03040_d6397596641e004d95d125cff1d5e: Inputs: input voltage and output current, which are externally controllable by the voltage source and load, respectively.
elements.2211.03040_ee2be26bc0233c54b2e791b982b4d: Outputs of the power converter are input current and output voltage, which are dependent on the input variables.
elements.2211.03040_a11fac639e8913faca86df610a647: It is impossible to determine a priori the precise configuration of a NARX-LSTM that matches the black-box dynamic properties since it depends on the dataset's parameters
